      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·魏風·004.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">陟岵.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>陟彼岵兮，瞻望父兮。父曰：「嗟予子！行役夙夜無已。上慎旃哉，猶來無止！」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>I ascend that tree-clad hill,
And look towards the residence of my father.
Morning and night never rests.
May he be careful,
That he may come back, and not remain there!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-weifeng-state-004__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
