      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·魏風·004.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">陟岵.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>陟彼屺兮，瞻望母兮。母曰：「嗟予季！行役夙夜無寐。上慎旃哉！猶來無棄！」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>I ascend that bare hill,
And look towards the residence of my mother.
Morning and night has no sleep.
May he be careful,
That he may come back, and not leave his body there!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
