      <prop type="x-translation-ref">陟岵.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>陟彼岡兮，瞻望兄兮。兄曰：「嗟予弟！行役夙夜必偕。上慎旃哉！猶來無死！」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>I ascend that ridge,
And look towards the residence of my elder brother.
My brother is saying, Alas! my younger brother, abroad on
the public service,
Morning and night must consort with his comrades.
May he be careful,
That he may come back, and not die!?</seg>
      </tuv>
